- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper applies AI techniques to NLP tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses neural networks for its models. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not the main focus, the paper mentions the use of embeddings, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks.
